reviewText: The dialog in this movie is amazing. I was totally blown away by this movie. It was so novel. I wish there were more movies like this. It touched on so many topics about relationships.
I was really impressed by the character work on Tre. This was a really great movie. I will be watching it again in the future.

Yes, lame as another review states, a bit like a TV Soapy, bought back memories of "The Young and the Restless'
Don't expect the excitement shown by the young lady on the cover.
With the exception maybe of McDowell, I don't know how they could assemble a more lame set of actors. The story was okay, but nothing new. It was about 80 minutes too long.
